comment:
* Indicates the errors that may occur at any point and are applicable to both
     * streaming and file-download.

variables.name: ERROR_MIDDLEWARE_NOT_YET_READY
ERROR_OUT_OF_MEMORY
variables.comment:
* Indicates that the middleware ran out of memory and was unable to complete the requested
         * operation.

variables.name: ERROR_MIDDLEWARE_TEMPORARILY_UNAVAILABLE
variables.comment:
* Indicates that the requested operation failed due to the middleware being unavailable due
         * to a transient condition. The app may retry the operation at a later time.

variables.name: ERROR_IN_E911
variables.comment:
* Indicates that the requested operation was not performed due to being in emergency
         * callback mode.

variables.name: ERROR_NOT_CONNECTED_TO_HOME_CARRIER_LTE
variables.comment: Indicates that MBMS is not available due to the device being in roaming.

variables.name: ERROR_UNABLE_TO_READ_SIM
variables.comment: Indicates that MBMS is not available due to a SIM read error.

variables.name: ERROR_CARRIER_CHANGE_NOT_ALLOWED
variables.comment:
* Indicates that MBMS is not available due to the inserted SIM being from an unsupported
         * carrier.
